        { "type": "textarea", "id": "card_1_body", "label": "Body", "default": "They cost more than most people expect - and that's fair. Every fiber and finish was chosen for performance, longevity, and health, not price. Yes, it's a higher upfront cost - but Jax Sheets are designed to last 5-10 years while staying soft, cool, and clean. Over time, they end up costing less than replacing cheaper sheets every year." },
