        { "type": "text", "id": "card_2_title", "label": "Title", "default": "Oil Stains Can Happen" },
        { "type": "textarea", "id": "card_2_body", "label": "Body", "default": "Jax Sheets are highly absorbent - that's part of what makes them breathable - but it also means they can hold onto oil from skin, hair, or skincare a bit more than cotton. Luckily, they wash out easily with proper care, and Jax 2.0 handles this better than ever but still not perfect." },
