        { "type": "text", "id": "card_3_title", "label": "Title", "default": "They Need Some Care When Washing" },
        { "type": "textarea", "id": "card_3_body", "label": "Body", "default": "Jax Sheets are performance fabrics, not indestructible gym towels. Avoid harsh soaps, bleach, fabric softeners and rough loads with jeans or zippers. Treat them right and they'll last up to a decade - ignore them and they'll last a few years." },
