        { "type": "textarea", "id": "card_5_body", "label": "Body", "default": "We once had a customer who lost his set of Jax Sheets in his divorce and others who plan their laundry day around being able to put Jax back on their bed, so you've been warned. Jax Sheets will ruin other sheets for you." },
